data.description: This home offers ample living space and endless possibilities. 3 living areas, including a formal on the 1st floor, a central living area with a cozy fireplace, and an upstairs living area or game room. Relax, entertain, or have space within your own home. The primary bedroom is on the1st floor and has an expansive en-suite bathroom and a walk-in closet with shelving all the way to the ceiling. Each of the 4 upstairs bedrooms are large, and have  walk-in closets. The 2 full bathrooms upstairs feature dual sinks, plus shower tub combos. The kitchen has newer appliances throughout, abundant counter and storage space. There is a walk-in pantry located in the utility room with room for an extra fridge, freezer, drip area.  Backyard has a covered patio with ceiling fan and seating area inviting you to unwind. Property ihas a water softener and filtration system, solar screens. Community offers access to a park, pool, and its conveniently located near several highways, close to NISD Schools.
